## 📊 Summary Comparison

| Task Attribute | High ACU Usage (Avoid) | Low ACU Usage (Optimal) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Scope** | "Build a whole feature." | "Implement this specific API endpoint." |
| **Context** | "Search the repo for how we do X." | "Refer to `file_path/example.py` for X." |
| **Testing** | "Make sure it works." | "Run `npm test` and verify output is 'Success'." |
| **Feedback** | Allowing unlimited autonomous retries. | Reviewing the plan and setting a session limit. |
